Authenticity is most powerful when aligned with ethics and vulnerability.

2. INTEGRITY: Integrity has such a wide spectrum that most entrepreneurs feel like they’re doing it wrong. You cannot do integrity wrong if you stick to the facts aka THE TRUTH.

This is HUGELY impactful to your willingness to be a spokesperson for yourself let alone the vocal advocate for your brand + business.

I wanted her bold, unapologetic way of being in the world. She wasn’t the most loving TV personality but I wasn’t watching her to learn how to love, I was watching her to learn how she held 1.6 million viewers.

Find inspiring characteristics in someone and practice talking like them, using their mannerisms and finding new parts of yourself.
